fullplot: For the first time ever, survivors of the famous 1972 Andes plane crash tell in their own words their harrowing story of survival.
plot: For the first time ever, survivors of the famous 1972 Andes plane crash tell in their own words their harrowing story of survival.
title: Stranded: I've Come from a Plane That Crashed on the Mountains
